Teach non-engraved projects how to retrive polyversion when pip-installed:

+ The functions :func:`.polyversion.polyversion()` & :func:`polyversion..polytime()`
  now attempt to fetch version from package/site-package infos.
+ And the function doing this :func:`polyversion.get_version_from_pkg_metadata()`
  retroffited to:
  + search for `<pname-<version>.egg-info/PKG-INFO` in `baspath` sibling folder
    (before PKG-INFO, METADATA in `basepath`),
  + so now `basepath` always needed n `polyversion()/polytime()` functions to
    locate sibling.